*{{cite news| first =| last =| authorlink =| author =| title =Current Report| trans_title =| url =http://investor.21cf.com/secfiling.cfm?filingid=1181431-13-22301| format =| newspaper =| location =| publisher =[[新闻集团_(1979－2013年)|News Corporation]]| agency =| id =| page =| date =April 16, 2013| accessdate =| language =| quote =| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160815103222/http://investor.21cf.com/secfiling.cfm?filingid=1181431-13-22301| archivedate =2016-08-15| dead-url =yes}}</ref>同年5月9日公開信發布新的公司標誌，象徵性的福斯探照燈變得更加現代化，<ref>{{cite news |author=Nikki Finke. |url=http://deadline.com/2013/05/rupert-murdoch-unveils-21st-century-fox-logo/ |title=Rupert Murdoch Unveils 21st Century Fox Logo: Video |publisher=Deadline.com |date=May 9, 2013 |accessdate= |archive-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010001155/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/rupert-murdoch-unveils-21st-century-fox-logo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 但21世紀福斯品牌不會延伸到20世紀福斯事業群，旗下事業部門照舊。<ref>Nikki Finke. [http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/no-name-change-for-20th-century-fox/ No Name Change for 20th Century Fox] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/no-name-change-for-20th-century-fox/ |date=20131029202411 }}. Deadline.com, April 16, 2013.</ref>舊新聞集團[[董事會|董事會]]於同年5月24日通過拆分計畫，並交付6月11日[[股東大會|股東大會]]通過。<ref>{{cite web |last=Wall |first=Matthew |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-22857106 |title=News Corp shareholders vote to split company into two |publisher=BBC News |date=2013-06-11 |accessdate=2013-06-11 |archive-date=2013-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613180411/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-22857106 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 同年6月28日拆分完成，公司正式成立；7月1日，股票重新在[[納斯達克|納斯達克]]上市。<ref name=lat-splitapproved>{{cite web|title=News Corp. board approves company split, set for June 28|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-news-corp-board-approves-company-split-28-20130524,0,2598197.story|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525155053/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-news-corp-board-approves-company-split-28-20130524,0,2598197.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2013/jun/18/rupert-murdoch-split-empire-news-corp?CMP=twt_fd |title=Rupert Murdoch splits empire but keeps faith in tomorrow's newspapers |publisher=[[衛報|衛報]] |date=2013-06-18 |accessdate=2013-06-18}}</ref><ref name=lat-splitvote>{{cite web|title=News Corp. plans June 11 shareholder vote on company split|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-news-corp-plans-june-11-shareholder-vote-on-company-split-20130430,0,2257797.story|work=洛杉磯時報|accessdate=2013-05-14|archive-date=2013-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130504085030/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-news-corp-plans-june-11-shareholder-vote-on-company-split-20130430,0,2257797.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bbc-splitofficial>{{cite web|title=News Corp officially splits in two|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-23104822|work=BBC News|accessdate=2013-06-29|archive-date=2013-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629032806/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-23104822|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年7月16日，默多克確認出價購買[[時代華納|時代華納]]公司，向時代華納出價800億美元，但是這項出價不包括時代華納旗下極具品牌價值的[[美國有線電視新聞網|美國有線電視新聞網]]。<ref>{{cite news|last1=SORKIN|first1=ANDREW ROSS|last2=DE LA MERCED|first2=MICHAEL J.|title=Rupert Murdoch Is Rebuffed in Offer for Time Warner|url=http://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/07/16/rupert-murdoch-said-to-have-made-offer-for-time-warner/?_php=true&_type=blogs&smid=tw-dealbook&seid=auto&_r=0|accessdate=July 16, 2014|work=New York Times|date=July 16, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806201854/https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/07/16/rupert-murdoch-said-to-have-made-offer-for-time-warner/?_php=true&_type=blogs&smid=tw-dealbook&seid=auto&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref> 7月25日，21世紀福斯宣佈將[[意大利天空廣播|意大利天空廣播]]和[[德國天空廣播|德國天空廣播]]以90億美元的價格賣給[[英國天空廣播|英國天空廣播]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/07/25/us-bskyb-europe-idUKKBN0FU0EE20140725 |title=BSkyB to pay $9 billion to create Sky Europe |publisher=Reuters |date=July 25, 2014 |accessdate=July 25, 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710093054/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/07/25/us-bskyb-europe-idUKKBN0FU0EE20140725 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 福斯將用這筆錢加上來自[[高盛|高盛]]的250億美元繼續進行與時代華納的交易。但8月5日福斯宣佈撤回這項投標。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-28668539 |title=21st Century Fox withdraws bid for Time Warner |publisher=BBC News |date=August 5, 2014 |accessdate=August 6, 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127182938/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-28668539 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 自福斯宣佈將進行這場交易後，其股價暴跌，其董事宣佈將在未來十二個月中回購60億美元的股份。<ref name="FoxCNN">{{cite news|title=Murdoch withdraws bid to acquire Time Warner|url=http://www.bignewsnetwork.com/index.php/sid/224460367|accessdate=7 August 2014|publisher=''Big News Network.com''|archive-date=2015-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128132806/http://www.bignewsnetwork.com/index.php/sid/224460367|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年9月11日，21世紀福斯以7.25億美元與[[國家地理學會|國家地理學會]]合資成立「國家地理合股有限責任公司」（National Geographic Partners, LLC.），並持有73%的股份。<ref name=verge-ngp>{{cite web|title=National Geographic magazine is now a for-profit business thanks to Fox|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/9/9/9296815/national-geographic-magazine-is-now-a-for-profit-business-fox|website=The Verge|accessdate=9 September 2015|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212071222/https://www.theverge.com/2015/9/9/9296815/national-geographic-magazine-is-now-a-for-profit-business-fox|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=National Geographic Society and 21st Century Fox Agree to Expand Partnership|url=http://press.nationalgeographic.com/2015/09/09/national-geographic-society-21st-century-fox-agree-to-expand-partnership/|website=NationalGeographic.com|accessdate=23 September 2015|archive-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316122514/http://press.nationalgeographic.com/2015/09/09/national-geographic-society-21st-century-fox-agree-to-expand-partnership/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年12月16日，21世紀福斯與英國[[天空公司|天空公司]]達成併購協議，21世紀福斯以117億英鎊（約148億美元）收購天空公司餘下的61%股權，而天空的股東就可獲得每股10.75英鎊的回報，整個併購行動涉及金額達185億英鎊。但英國競爭及市場署（Competition and Markets Authority，CMA）於2018年1月23日暫行裁定該項交易會賦予梅鐸家族過多新聞掌控權、不符公眾利益，除非天空新聞台（Sky News）的問題能解決。<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/cma-provisionally-finds-foxsky-deal-not-in-the-public-interest |script-title=CMA provisionally finds Fox/Sky deal not in the public interest |publisher=Competition and Markets Authority |via= |author= |language= |date=2018-01-23 |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125022640/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/cma-provisionally-finds-foxsky-deal-not-in-the-public-interest |archivedate=2018-01-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 再度拆分 ===
{{main|迪士尼收購21世紀福斯}}
2017年12月14日，21世紀福斯與[[華特迪士尼公司|華特迪士尼公司]]達成協議，迪士尼以0.2745股股份換1股21世紀福斯股份，每股交易作價相當於29.54美元，即斥資524億美元收購21世紀福斯旗下有線電視及影視業務，包括影視製作公司、地區體育網絡、[[福斯傳媒集團|福-{}-斯傳媒集團]]、[[FX_(电视频道)|FX頻道]]以及[[國家地理頻道|國家地理頻道]]等等，亦取得福斯持有的[[Hulu|Hulu]]與[[天空公司|天空公司]]股份；此外，迪士尼將會承擔21世紀福斯的137億美元淨債務。<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.21cf.com/news/21st-century-fox/2017/walt-disney-company-acquire-twenty-first-century-fox-inc-after-spinoff |title=The Walt Disney Company to Acquire Twenty-First Century Fox, Inc., After Spinoff of Certain Businesses, for $52.4 Billion in Stock |publisher=21st Century Fox |date=2017-12-14 |accessdate= |via= |archive-date=2017-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215000630/https://www.21cf.com/news/21st-century-fox/2017/walt-disney-company-acquire-twenty-first-century-fox-inc-after-spinoff |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=https://thewaltdisneycompany.com/walt-disney-company-acquire-twenty-first-century-fox-inc-spinoff-certain-businesses-52-4-billion-stock/ |title=The Walt Disney Company To Acquire Twenty-First Century Fox, Inc., After Spinoff Of Certain Businesses, For $52.4 Billion In Stock |publisher=The Walt Disney Company |date=2017-12-14 |accessdate= |via= |archive-date=2017-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171219072155/https://thewaltdisneycompany.com/walt-disney-company-acquire-twenty-first-century-fox-inc-spinoff-certain-businesses-52-4-billion-stock/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但該項交易還得過《[[反托拉斯法|反托拉斯法]]》這一關才算完成<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2017/12/14/disney-to-buy-21st-century-fox-assets.html|title=Disney to buy 21st Century Fox assets in a deal worth more than $52 billion in stock|last=Castillo|first=Michelle|work=CNBC|date=2017-12-14|accessdate=2017-12-14|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214133050/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/12/14/disney-to-buy-21st-century-fox-assets.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

若交易順利，21世紀福斯的剩餘資產包括[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]、[[福斯廣播公司|福斯廣播公司]]、[[福斯財經網|福斯財經網]]、[[福斯美國頻道|福斯美國頻道]]、[[FOX_Sports|FOX Sports]]及[[十大联盟|十大联盟]]電視網，將分拆成一間新的[[福斯公司|福斯公司]]，仍使用「福斯」（Fox）品牌。分拆前，新福斯將向21世紀福斯支付85億美元現金股息，新公司將維持之前的A、B股結構。分拆後，21世紀福斯的股東將按之前所持有的股份類別，收到相同數量的新福斯股份。<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.21cf.com/news/21st-century-fox/2017/21st-century-fox-spin-businesses-create-new-fox-growth-company |title=21st Century Fox to Spin off Businesses and Create New "Fox"; A Growth Company Centered on Live News and Sports Brands and the Iconic Fox Brand |publisher=21st Century Fox |date=2017-12-14 |accessdate= |via= |archive-date=2018-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180106172838/https://www.21cf.com/news/21st-century-fox/2017/21st-century-fox-spin-businesses-create-new-fox-growth-company |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2018年5月10日，二十一世紀福斯以9.1億美元收購美國辛克萊廣播集團（{{lang|en|Sinclair Broadcast Group}}）旗下7家地方電視台。6月20日，迪士尼將收購21世紀福斯資產的價格提高至每股38美元，總價約達713億美元現金加股票。7月27日21世紀福克斯和迪士尼股東今日批准了迪士尼收購21世紀福克斯的交易。10月4日，21世紀福斯以151億美元出售持有的英國[[天空公司|天空公司]]（Sky）39.1%股權給[[康卡斯特|康卡斯特]]。

2019年3月20日，併購正式完成，资产整合进[[華特迪士尼公司|華特迪士尼公司]]的各个部门<ref>{{Cite web|title=Disney’s Acquisition of 21st Century Fox Will Bring an Unprecedented Collection of Content and Talent to Consumers Around the World|url=https://www.thewaltdisneycompany.com/disneys-acquisition-of-21st-century-fox-will-bring-an-unprecedented-collection-of-content-and-talent-to-consumers-around-the-world/|work=The Walt Disney Company|date=2019-03-19|accessdate=2019-03-20|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190319220812/https://www.thewaltdisneycompany.com/disneys-acquisition-of-21st-century-fox-will-bring-an-unprecedented-collection-of-content-and-talent-to-consumers-around-the-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

